            <td>Routes MCP server calls through a unified HTTP gateway</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><a href="https://github.com/github/gh-aw-actions" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">gh-aw-actions ↗</a></td>
            <td>Shared library of custom Actions used by compiled workflows</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h2>Continuous AI</h2>
      <p><code>gh-aw</code> enables what GitHub Next calls <strong>Continuous AI</strong> — systematic, automated application of AI to software collaboration. Common patterns include:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Keeping documentation current automatically</li>
        <li>Incrementally improving code quality</li>
        <li>Intelligently triaging issues and PRs</li>
        <li>Automating code review</li>
        <li>Maintaining research knowledge bases (AgentPages)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

